<!-- Node: "Games industry is running out of ideas." -->
<div class="body_box_header">Games industry is running out of ideas.</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/204" title="View user profile.">Miniwood</a> on Tuesday, March 30, 2004 - 19:51</small><br /><br />
Reuters reports that industry insiders at the game Developers Conference in San Jose, California are concerned that there are no new ideas in the industry which is now dominated by sequels and film tie-ins.<br />
<br />
